title: The Gary Null Show
content:
Health Updates: power walking, Alzheimer’s; benefits of vegan, vegetarian diet; homeopathy; obesity, depression &... <!--more--> physical activity; broccoli juice- sulforaphane; walking daily cuts risk of disease; tomatoes vs prostate cancer Commentary: looking back on 2010- crack-pot economics, health-less healthcare, the BP oil spill, S510- are we becoming a police state?
